# iCloud test credentials — defense in depth so they can never be committed.
# These would normally live OUTSIDE the repo at e.g. `~/.config/secrets/`,
# but if they ever end up inside the repo path (test-tempdir mishap, etc.)
# git must refuse to add them.
**/icloud-username*
**/icloud-app-password*
**/icloud-test-creds*
